lead_paragraph: Crystal Palace continued winning in the F.A. Cup while struggling in the Premier League as Yohan Cabaye and Fraizer Campbell scored late goals to beat second-tier Reading, 2-0, in the quarterfinals.

headline.main: Crystal Palace Advances in F.A. Cup

abstract: Crystal Palace beats Reading, 2-0, in FA Cup quarterfinal match.
